    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Fully configurable, pillow-top, with built in vibration functionality, hardness settings, actuated joints, self-heating <em>and</em> self-cooling componentry, a proprietary Sleep Model learning AI, self-regulating SheetShare technology, and patented WaveMotion shock absorbers and \"action enhancers\" for when you put that Mr. Studd to use. The King Henry IV of mattresses, produced by a NC-local mattress firm called New Royalty that went bankrupt during CW4 after Militech accidentally firebombed the company's factory and Arasaka subsumed and dismantled the insurance company which would have allowed them to recover. Sleep like the lord you are.</p><p>One is included with each room rented on the 4th floor of the Afterlife, and stored by the hotel, free of charge, if removed. All others must be purchased using HQ IP.</p><p>Allows a room to sleep up to 2 edgerunners comfortably, or 1 edgerunner with a body of 8 or higher. After spending a night on the mattress, the user's first check the following day gets a +1 bonus.</p>"
    },
